{"tid":468940,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽忍手靜待騰訊季績","createTime":"2017-11-15T00:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T00:00:29.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e065e20dc46ea36afa945cac93552a040af91982","tid":468940,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T00:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171114/photo/bkn-20171114180127176-1114_00842_001_01b.jpg?20171114180423\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171114180127176-1114_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20171114180423&h=93259d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港股高位表現反覆，昨日恒指收報29,152點，跌30點，主板成交達1,082億元。港股通成交額144.4億元，較上日減少17億元，佔主板成交額的13%；南下資金淨流入減少50%至24.99億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊控股(00700)高位阻力不輕，今日(14日)收報388元，升0.4元，港股通淨買入約1,762萬元，淨買入之少為近期少見。<br />\n<br />\n石油股早前轉強，但近日動力一般，中國石油化工(00386)今日更跌1.5%，港股通淨賣出約2.61億元，為港股通淨賣出最大個股。<br />\n<br />\n新華保險(01336)近期轉強，今日逆市升0.2%，港股通淨買入約1.58億元。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171114/photo/bkn-20171114180127176-1114_00842_001_02b.jpg?20171114180423\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171114180127176-1114_00842_001_02b.jpg%3F20171114180423&h=cb3b341d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港股通(滬)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171114/photo/bkn-20171114180127176-1114_00842_001_03b.jpg?20171114180423\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171114180127176-1114_00842_001_03b.jpg%3F20171114180423&h=4a1e513a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港股通(深)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171114/bkn-20171114180127176-1114_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171114%2Fbkn-20171114180127176-1114_00842_001.html&d=qmgJ4JsaQLd0Qrc9uKAAV8VakpCEQgWe